name: "MerryChristmas"
description:
here is a sweet little A6 [C6] card i drew on using a blue biro, and coloured in using Berol felt tip pens. the card is a white colour and is textured and will come with a matching white envelope and in a cellophane bag.

the card is blank inside, and has a stamped 'cards by clarebear' logo on the back!

all cards are designed and hand-drawn by me, so eash is unique!

i love doing custom designs, so contact me here or on twitter @cLare_beaR_

x
